summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 5864 for the improvement of The Alley in Block 8, Bell and Denny's Addition, being the alley between Western Avenue and Elliott Avenue from Vine Street to Cedar Street; by paving and otherwise improving the same; under Ordinance No. 77258, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
